Kogi State Governor Yahaya Bello, has expressed confidence in winning the presidential ticket of the All Progressives Congress (APC) for the 2023 elections. The Governor disclosed this on Monday while speaking on Channels Television’s Sunrise Daily, stating that after his emergence as the presidential candidate, other zoning arrangements will sort themselves out naturally. Bello said, “I am confident my party, the APC will give me the chance to fly the flag of the party. “By the grace of God, after my emergence as the presidential candidate, every other zoning arrangement will sort itself out naturally, just like what you saw at the Eagle Square on Saturday. “By the grace of God, we are going to pass through democratic process; consensus is part of it, voting is part of it, but I am confident that whichever way you go by, our party will come out the best by electing me as the flag bearer of the APC.”